# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:86
translate russian juliana4_8632d269:

    # "We walk out to my car together and quickly leave the café."
    "Мы вместе выходим к моей машине и быстро уезжаем из кафе."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:87
translate russian juliana4_f37f2114:

    # "She doesn't talk much on the way, except to point me towards her house."
