# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:103
translate russian juliana4_647112e1:

    # "I could have gone inside with her and that might have led to other things."
    "Я мог бы зайти с ней, и это могло бы привести к чему-то еще."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:104
translate russian juliana4_b43224db:

    # "But I wasn't very interested in Juliana in that way."
    "Но я не был особо заинтересован в Джулиане в этом смысле."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:105
translate russian juliana4_74079974:

    # "I hope I didn't hurt her feelings."
